Shots were fired late last night at a residential area in Shinjuku.
Several of what appear to be bullet holes were found in the vicinity,
with some of them in a bicycle that was abandoned at the scene of the crime.
Shots fired in the city No casualties
Shots fired in the city No casualties
The police are looking for its owner, believing them to be involved in the incident.
Well, I guess it is got nothing to do with me.
Multiple late-night robberies and muggings have been reported in the area recently.
The police are investigating if these are related to last night's shooting.
Wow, that is practically our neighborhood.
Is not that close to where you work?
There was an earthquake in the Kantou region.
I really feel like there is going to be another earthquake.
Um, if it is fine with you, could we meet up and talk about this?
I really feel like there is going to be another earthquake.
Um, if it is fine with you,
could we meet up and talk about this?
I am off work tomorrow anyway, and you do not have a shift either, right?
I am off work tomorrow anyway,
and you do not have a shift either, right?
Do you have work today, Chiho?
This area's been pretty dangerous lately.
Oh, that is what you meant.
What else would I be talking about?
Hey, the shooting on the news this morning was pretty close to your place, was not it?
Nah, it happened three stations away.
Anyway, what is going on for lunch?
Want To go to that curry place we talked about the other day?
We might have to line up, though.
I do not have the time to stand in line today.
I need to take care of a mountain of paperwork during lunch.
Sounds like you have totally gotten used to life in Japan,
Could you state your name, please?
Someone who knows both the Hero and the Overlord.
And someone who is planning to destroy both of you in one fell swoop.
were you the one who repeatedly tried to access the servers late last night?
I never thought the Hero and the Overlord would team up in a fight.
We are extremely ashamed of what has happened.
Anyway, Overlord Satan, who traveled to another world,
shall be eliminated along with Hero Emilia.
I-I am sorry, but we will not have an answer for you until it has been investigated on our end.
The fact that the Hero and Overlord both ran away with their tails between their legs?
I would be very interested in the findings.
This vulgar voice sounds like it is echoing in darkness.
I am pretty sure Alsiel was the only one who survived out of the four generals.
I can tell you want to provoke me by calling it Ente Isla's will and whatnot,
but a demon's rantings are of no importance to me.
It is too bad I cannot get you to believe me.
I will get in touch soon.
There are all sorts of people in this world, are not there?
The bank's probably jam-packed right now, anyway.
This is the Yoyogi Police Department.
Man, who knew they would sniff us out using just my bicycle?
Japanese cops are not half bad!
It turned out we were right though, were not we?
The Hero had indeed cooked up her age.
If I am not mistaken, her real age is somewhere around seventeen or eighteen.
I knew she would have registered herself to be over twenty.
Wait, do not people usually cook up a younger age?
How do you even cook up an age?
Why do I, the Hero, have to be the guarantor for the Overlord?!
W-We did not have a choice.
We did not particularly want to rely on you for this either.
You think I was expecting to use my seal and ID for something like this?!
Well, we also could have asked my boss...
Yeah, but you do not want to cause problems for her, do you?
Oh, but you do for me?!
What kind of Overlord does not because problems for the Hero?
Still, why would you choose me?
Come on, I even gave you a place to sleep last night.
You are acting more pathetic than heroic.
Like you are one to talk, Alsiel!
What the hell was up with that empty fridge?!
Why do not you plan your purchases out properly?
It is not even my fault...
I just got a threatening phone call at work.
I am being targeted, but Maou,
Do not say I did not warn you.
But mark my words: I will be the one to kill you.
You should keep in mind that you are in public right now.
make sure you do not let some no-name loser kill you before I take your head!
Not to mention, they called her, huh?
But it is not even my fault...
I have been managing our expenses perfectly...
I have to go meet Chiho soon too.
When and where are you meeting this Sasaki person,
and when will you be getting home?
I am meeting her at the east entrance of Shinjuku Station at five.
You have still got some time.
Wait, where did we even get the money to buy these clothes?
I have got some secret savings for rainy days such as these.
Yeah, we are meeting up, but I am only going to get some coffee, talk to her, then leave.
I do not really need to dress up
A young lady would not tell anyone but her most trusted friends about her serious worries!
And yet, she told you about it!
I am sure you know what that means, right?
I cannot let you go on a date wearing just Uniclo stuff.
Apologize to the number one brand in the fashion industry, Uniclo, and to me!
Did you cut your hair, Chiho?
I got it trimmed a little.
I thought you would be wearing Uniclo again, but...
There is nothing wrong with Uniclo!
But you look cooler than usual today.
My roommate insisted I could not possibly wear Uniclo on a date.
So you consider this a date?
Let us go to Cafe Dotour.
It is cheap, and we can relax there.
I am the one asking you for advice,
so I will pick up the tab!
Do not look down on me.
I can take care of this.
Yeah, we might get separated if we do not.
There is a lot of people here.
I kind of knew you were going to say that.
Stop calling me by my real name.
You are acting mighty suspicious right now.
That is none of your business!
Do you really think I, the Hero, would ignore you guys after seeing you act all suspicious?
Could you overlook this so I do not lose face?
That demonic face you had back in Ente Isla?
I would much rather you lost it.
I am so very sorry, Milord.
What are you planning to do to that girl, you scumbag!?
You have got the wrong idea!
Milord has not a single evil intention in mind!
What kind of overlord does not have evil intentions?!
Oh, so that is what it was about.
The only thing I understand is that my archnemesis has fallen to an extremely pathetic state.
Still, why does he have to go on a date?
That is what I thought too.
However, it seems that Sasaki girl has considerable feelings for Milord.
You do not have anything to say about that?
I just found it extremely insolent that a mere human girl would even think about falling in love with Milord.
I am wondering why such a cute girl would fall for a good-for-nothing loser like him.
Well, I am the Hero, after all.
Anyway, there is not a single woman out there that could not tell you what is going on at a glance.
She is wearing a dress that is all the rage this summer.
Her hair looks like she just came from the hairdresser's.
But of course guys would not get it.
The material gives off a fresh feeling of summer,
and with that fit, she is emphasizing her body shap
Being big does not serve any purpose in battles.
Plus, the smaller you are, the cheaper plate armor is.
And it is easier to move around too!
What the hell are you talking about?
You guys think you can figure something out by talking to her?
I am just following them to make sure there are not suspicious characters wandering around.
You are by far the most suspicious one here.
However, what she said about the earthquakes does bother me a little.
If her situation has anything at all to do with our world, then...
There is no point in standing guard here.
To the cafe they are in, of course!
How could I possibly explain such a bold and audacious move to Milord later
So, could you give me the details one more time?
I told you about how my ears started ringing real bad around the time I started working at MgRonald's, right?
At first, I thought I was just tired because I was doing something I was not used to.
I guess no one can hear me after all.
Only a select few can receive this, anyway.
I am sure some strange incidents are happening in your world.
There might be a big one
in the near future, so be careful.
We will pick the right time
I would never even heard that language before, but I understood what they were saying.
I did not know what was going on.
So you reached the conclusion that they had to be talking about the earthquakes.
That was the communication technique used to synchronize
the minds of humans in different worlds to share ideas and concepts,
An Idea Link is formed using a probe technique.
The probe, called a Sonar, is released.
The Sonar causes a magic explosion once it reaches its destination,
which manifests as various kinds of phenomena.
In this case, it is pretty likely that it manifested as an earthquake.
If we consider the because for these recent earthquakes around us
being Sonars sent out in order to investigate what we and Emilia were up to,
There might be a big one in the near future, huh?
Looks like things are moving much faster than I anticip
Why did Emi just walk in here with Ashiya?!
I have not done anything wrong.
Anyway, judging by what you just said,
the ear-ringing and weird voices are not really an issue.
What is important is whether a big one will really happen or not.
When it comes down to it,
I think just urging people around you to be careful can really change how things turn out.
I knew you were the right person to ask about this.
I feel like I got a lot off my chest.
I have not done anything wrong!
No matter which way you look at this, I am being a wonderful colleague!
I could not tell my friends, parents, or anyone else about this.
But I thought you would believe me.
Nothing good will come out of getting involved with this man.
He is nothing like what he seems to be.
He is wicked and cruel deep down.
D-Do not just show up and say such awful things!
What are you to Maou, anyway?!
Getting involved with him will only bring you pain and sorrow.
Do not you dare tell me what to do.
You came to MgRonald's the other day, did not you?
Are you Maou's ex-girlfriend or something?
What the hell are you saying?!
In that case, I can make my move on Maou however I want!
It is none of your business now!
Can you stop being so stupid?
Then why do you keep hanging around him?
Our relationship is too complicated to talk about!
Are you trying to say you are more intimate with him?
How can you even interpret it that way?!
There is no other way I could interpret it!
He is not here, at the very least.
That is not what I meant.
You are worried he got crushed by the debris?
Well, there are a lot of people who would rejoice if he died here,
And I am going to be the one to kill him.
I will not let him die like this.
I am sure he is fine.
there really is nothing between Maou and me.
I will believe you for now.
What do you even see in Maou?
You picked a fight with me because you love him, right?
Is it that easy to tell?
Anyone could tell just by looking at you.
How do you feel about Maou?
Close to him is the last thing I would want to be.
Well, we certainly do go way back.
You are bound to get hurt if you love him.
Do not say I did not warn you.
I do not really get what you are saying.
You will find out soon enough.
Actually, it might be better if you did not.
Anyway, just take a little nap.
I know you are here somewhere.
Why do you look like that?
By the time I noticed, I was already like this.
Good grief, how am I supposed to explain away how I look?
I can still use the last of my powers and summon my sacred sword to kill him.
but we cannot just sit around and wait to be rescued.
I will do something about this.
Where in this silent sky does the sun rise?
A promise I made while pretending to not see it
Being a liar and a coward
If I was at fault for everything
Then our promise might only have been a fleeting dream
I managed to hide it in the shadow of the moonlight
My tears will not flow anymore
If I was able to let everything go
I might be able to cry again
But this world is full of things I want to protect
